 take on the five fearsome Lords of Ire, up the challenge by seeking out uniquely monstrous dark & powerful creatures, lurking in each level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/70d9f78d2d6e7afad24ccb62678889e1.poster.avif?t=1716972671\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/70d9f78d2d6e7afad24ccb62678889e1.webm?t=1716972671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/70d9f78d2d6e7afad24ccb62678889e1.mp4?t=1716972671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/f83743586626e902eff0dc9fc124e6ae.avif?t=1716972671\" width=612 height=102 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore diverse environments across five unique lands filled with nightmarish visions and stomach-churning creatures.<br></li><li>Experiment with different playstyles using a variety of weapon styles, runes & blessings<br></li><li>Fight to preserve your sanity, or succumb to the madness and harness it…<br></li><li>Test your skills against horrific enemies, dark monstrosities and epic boss battles with the mighty Lords of Ire.<br></li><li>Fully realise the horrors of Morbid as the series steps into a new 3D perspective.</li></ul>",
